<p class="govuk-body">This factsheet explains what to do if:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
<li>you, your partner, your child or children go abroad permanently</li>
<li>you go abroad permanently, but your partner, your child or children stay in the UK</li>
<li>you, your partner, your child or children go abroad temporarily</li>
<li>you have a child who lives abroad</li>
<li>you or your partner are posted abroad as a Crown Servant</li>
</ul>

<p class="govuk-body">Factsheets are for guidance only and reflect the HMRC position at the time of writing.</p>